{"tid":827791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"配合航母建造速度　解放軍急聘艦載機飛行員","createTime":"2018-09-19T07:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T14:27:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d2a9998191ad034e2bde728bfb83b7615830a61","tid":827791,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"2018年09月19日 12:07<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3243/d3243033.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3243%2Fd3243033.jpg&h=eab4bb65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲解放軍殲-15戰機。（圖／大陸國防部網站）<br />\n記者蔡浩祥／綜合報導<br />\n大陸《解放軍報》今報導，解放軍海軍於16日啟動了2019年度招飛工作，將派出4個招飛工作組分赴大陸全國23個省、市、自治區，選拔飛行學員苗子。據悉，應該與第二艘航母下水，及今後航母擴建計畫有關。<br />\n報導指出，本次招募重點突出「艦載機飛行學員」招收選拔，海軍飛行員招收由「岸基」向「艦載」轉變，以全面構建具有海軍特色、適應艦載要求的招飛體系。<br />\n海軍招飛辦領導說，按艦載機飛行員標準選拔出的優秀學員，將有機會駕駛「飛鯊」（殲-15）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3243/d3243043.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3243%2Fd3243043.jpg&h=8ed5d6ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲解放軍海軍航母遼寧艦。（圖／大陸國防部網站）<br />\n截至目前，解放軍已擁有兩艘航母，一艘是以「瓦良格」號航母為基礎改造的「遼寧艦」；另一艘則是自行建造，與「遼寧艦」同等級航母，正在下水測試中，而這兩艘航艦都採用常規滑躍式起飛。<br />\n資料顯示，解放軍海軍航空兵部隊於2013年5月組建；媒體報導，2015年底，新一批殲15艦載戰機飛行員駕機完成觸艦復飛、阻攔著艦等多個課目訓練。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180919/1262123.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180919%2F1262123.htm&d=vWTFKYeVB2iqjjbcuzELvIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=79fff5fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180919/1262123.htm</a>"},{"pid":"98240d23bbae6670f6c23209297590a39eabed3d","tid":827791,"uid":32511,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:49:09.000Z","msg":"急聘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n骨場請技c咩，話請就請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45aecc0a0f398d957d429e97b8a6db032c89808","tid":827791,"uid":208981,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"遲d赢國出咗班9G頂唔到15秒的機師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b801206c4ce9f2c1f5fa0548df151814666a5a","tid":827791,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:40:01.000Z","msg":"係邊到請？battlefield 入面？<br />\ncheat 架wo"},{"pid":"b587a7b1de21fc2d39320e6e45dd554b764b74eb","tid":827791,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"98240d23bbae6670f6c23209297590a39eabed3d","tid":827791,"uid":32511,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:49:09.000Z","msg":"急聘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n骨場請技c咩，話請就請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:47:34.000Z","msg":"預左做神風死士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6213dc7a1528da552280048e4930c147e2f3dfb3","tid":827791,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T10:00:29.000Z","msg":"機械器具測試員（九死一生）！"},{"pid":"c5f820582287f96803e37b40466b9bb2969d0e2e","tid":827791,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T10:03:18.000Z","msg":"常規動力，仲要係滑躍式，一個字：垃